data.description: Spacious three-bedroom Rancher, ideally situated on a corner lot within the coveted Highland MD community! This home boasts updated kitchen and bathrooms, great space for entertaining or dishing up something special just for you!  Step outside to relax on the maintenance-free deck or indulge in the pool. Photos of open pool are from 2021. The expansive yard features  an invisible pet fence and four fully grown Blueberry Bushes, offering delicious berries in July/August. Additionally, enjoy the convenience of a 30x30 detached garage, ideal for working on your car or pursuing hobbies. Schedule your showing today to fully appreciate all this home has to offer!
